sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User/Browser
    participant N as Node/TypeScript Gateway
    participant P as Python Worker
    participant O as OpenAI APIs

    U->>N: Audio input over WebSocket
    N->>P: Forward process_audio request
    P->>O: Transcription request
    O-->>P: Transcript text
    P->>O: LLM response request
    O-->>P: Assistant response text
    P->>O: TTS request
    O-->>P: Audio output
    P-->>N: Transcript + assistant text + audio
    N-->>U: Return transcript + text + audio
